   abduction of a young mother. Barclay has to defend the course of his
   enquiry to an independent 28-day police review comprised of detectives
   from outside the local force. Kyle has been charged with Rosie&#039;s
   abduction but maintains he never touched her and claims to know nothing
   about Leanne&#039;s disappearance. It is Matt&#039;s birthday, and over the past
   few weeks he&#039;s grown close to the attentive Sarah.
